WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 32=

01:49.060 --> 01:51.860
(Three days later)

03:42.830 --> 03:44.140
You're not what you used to be.

03:46.670 --> 03:47.510
Fine.

03:49.020 --> 03:50.700
I'll give you some more days to recover.

04:00.110 --> 04:01.140
He Simu,

04:03.900 --> 04:05.460
you'll never get the truth

04:06.300 --> 04:07.830
you've been seeking.

04:37.300 --> 04:38.420
Why didn't you tell me

04:38.550 --> 04:40.110
before you returned this time?

04:40.470 --> 04:41.820
I would have welcomed you.

04:43.670 --> 04:45.030
You are well-informed.

04:45.230 --> 04:46.910
You came when I just arrived.

04:49.860 --> 04:50.700
Simu,

04:51.300 --> 04:52.620
when you're back this time,

04:53.060 --> 04:54.420
you look different.

04:57.790 --> 04:59.180
Very good.

04:59.710 --> 05:00.670
It's been centuries.

05:01.180 --> 05:02.990
Congratulations on getting your beloved.

05:05.150 --> 05:05.990
Simu,

05:06.350 --> 05:07.740
the mist in your eyes is gone.

05:14.740 --> 05:17.350
Since when did I have that?

05:19.230 --> 05:20.120
Every spirit

05:20.120 --> 05:21.350
has a specific obsession.

05:22.110 --> 05:23.710
He knows why he lives

05:23.710 --> 05:24.790
and why he disappears.

05:25.990 --> 05:27.180
Even though those are not

05:27.180 --> 05:28.860
very decent obsessions.

05:29.470 --> 05:30.310
But Simu,

05:30.550 --> 05:31.740
you're born a spirit.

05:32.230 --> 05:34.110
There was always a mist in your eyes.

05:35.550 --> 05:36.390
Now,

05:36.550 --> 05:37.740
your heart is finally settled.

05:38.230 --> 05:39.260
I'm really happy for you.

05:48.230 --> 05:50.150
Yan Ke must not know this.

05:51.030 --> 05:52.550
He has feelings for you.

05:53.230 --> 05:54.910
What if his love grows into hate?

05:54.910 --> 05:57.030
He might hurt your man. Be careful.

05:58.790 --> 05:59.740
But it's all right.

06:00.150 --> 06:01.260
Recently,

06:01.260 --> 06:02.590
he's been terribly busy.

06:02.860 --> 06:04.860
He travels between the two worlds.

06:05.110 --> 06:06.110
No time for jealousy.

06:10.380 --> 06:11.790
Why does he go to the Mortal World?

06:13.620 --> 06:15.150
We don't know why,

06:15.500 --> 06:16.420
but for a few months,

06:16.420 --> 06:18.230
no spirits came from Shuozhou.

06:18.230 --> 06:20.670
We thought some spirits
wanted to linger there.

06:20.670 --> 06:22.230
So we sent Spirit Officials.

06:22.380 --> 06:24.260
But they didn't find anything unusual.

06:24.500 --> 06:26.030
After that, Yan Ke went many times

06:26.030 --> 06:27.180
to Shuozhou to investigate.

06:27.860 --> 06:28.740
Shuozhou.

06:30.260 --> 06:33.060
(Sovereign's Hall)

06:35.030 --> 06:36.350
When did Her Grace come back?

06:37.300 --> 06:38.140
Who knows?

06:38.550 --> 06:39.860
Her Grace loved excitement.

06:40.620 --> 06:41.860
But now she has returned

06:41.860 --> 06:42.700
so quietly.

06:43.820 --> 06:45.350
Anything abnormal often means trouble.

06:45.590 --> 06:46.620
We must be careful.

06:53.940 --> 06:55.740
Greetings, Your Grace.

06:56.590 --> 06:57.430
You may rise.

07:00.670 --> 07:01.940
In the Mortal World,

07:01.940 --> 07:02.780
I executed a sinner

07:02.800 --> 07:03.990
who was on the run for years.

07:04.740 --> 07:06.740
It's the Lord of Jiling Temple,

07:07.180 --> 07:08.020
Song Xingyu.

07:08.670 --> 07:09.620
Song Xingyu?

07:09.620 --> 07:10.790
He manipulated mortals,

07:11.180 --> 07:12.620
interfered with mortal affairs,

07:13.060 --> 07:14.300
and violated our decrees.

07:14.990 --> 07:16.590
I executed him on the spot

07:16.590 --> 07:17.470
and annihilated him.

07:18.620 --> 07:19.740
I hope all of you

07:20.860 --> 07:21.990
will take this as a warning.

07:30.740 --> 07:32.060
How wise you are, Your Grace.

07:35.500 --> 07:37.350
How wise you are, Your Grace.

07:40.620 --> 07:41.460
Yan Ke,

07:42.150 --> 07:43.790
you're in charge of the North Abyss.

07:44.590 --> 07:45.710
How is everything?

07:46.470 --> 07:48.350
Sorry for my poor supervision.

07:49.030 --> 07:50.060
Three days ago, it was hit

07:50.060 --> 07:51.380
by an undersea earthquake.

07:51.620 --> 07:53.260
There was a partial collapse.

07:53.910 --> 07:55.820
Some spirits have been trapped.

07:56.020 --> 07:57.190
- Now...
- It collapsed?

07:57.470 --> 07:58.910
We are still searching for them.

07:59.420 --> 08:01.260
Why didn't you report this

08:02.110 --> 08:03.110
until I asked you?

08:06.230 --> 08:07.740
Don't be angry, Your Grace.

08:08.710 --> 08:10.060
Not many spirits are missing.

08:10.550 --> 08:12.620
And I'm sparing no effort
in searching for them.

08:13.470 --> 08:14.820
Punish me as you wish.

08:15.620 --> 08:16.470
Yan Ke,

08:18.550 --> 08:20.990
I gave you the right
to supervise the Void,

08:21.820 --> 08:23.110
but you did a poor job,

08:23.110 --> 08:24.620
causing some spirits to suffer.

08:24.790 --> 08:25.820
This is your first sin.

08:26.910 --> 08:27.940
Second,

08:28.670 --> 08:29.790
you showed no respect

08:29.790 --> 08:31.300
and decided without my permission.

08:31.550 --> 08:32.590
Acting on your own

08:32.590 --> 08:33.860
is the sin of usurpation.

08:37.660 --> 08:38.860
You'll be flogged 50 times

08:39.140 --> 08:40.070
and grounded ten days.

08:40.310 --> 08:41.150
Immediately.

08:46.950 --> 08:47.790
Your Grace,

08:48.020 --> 08:49.900
thank you for the punishment.

09:16.860 --> 09:17.900
It's just a little problem.

09:18.470 --> 09:19.990
Isn't the punishment too harsh?

09:20.430 --> 09:21.990
Her Grace decides

09:22.860 --> 09:24.430
who to punish or whether to punish him.

10:20.620 --> 10:21.460
Simu,

10:23.020 --> 10:25.110
I've prepared new entertainment for you.

10:26.020 --> 10:27.620
You'll love it.

10:31.140 --> 10:32.260
I'd like to see

10:32.260 --> 10:34.190
how much you care about that mortal.

10:44.460 --> 10:46.580
(Shuozhou)

11:02.060 --> 11:04.140
(Chongxing Store)

11:15.990 --> 11:17.140
So that's it.

11:22.980 --> 11:24.220
(Liang)

11:29.110 --> 11:29.950
Xu,

11:30.140 --> 11:31.830
I sneaked into Youzhou and scouted.

11:32.020 --> 11:33.380
The Chong's deployments vary

11:33.380 --> 11:34.780
in the morning, noon, and evening.

11:35.230 --> 11:36.230
I sketched three versions

11:36.230 --> 11:37.070
of their deployments.

11:38.470 --> 11:39.950
The one in the evening

11:39.950 --> 11:41.470
is the same as what you saw last time.

11:41.660 --> 11:42.590
But it varies greatly

11:42.590 --> 11:44.020
in the other two periods.

11:46.990 --> 11:47.830
Very good.

11:47.830 --> 11:49.620
All we need is Xia Qingsheng's backup.

11:50.620 --> 11:51.460
When will he be back?

11:52.110 --> 11:53.260
News came this morning.

11:53.540 --> 11:54.430
Commandant Xia

11:54.430 --> 11:56.260
recruited troops smoothly in Shenzhou.

11:56.740 --> 11:57.950
Now, he's on his way back.

11:58.110 --> 11:58.950
I guess soon,

11:58.970 --> 11:59.860
he will join us.

12:03.140 --> 12:03.980
Where's Han Lingqiu?

12:07.540 --> 12:08.830
General Tang of the uprising army

12:08.830 --> 12:09.780
needs backup in Jingzhou.

12:10.350 --> 12:11.430
Captain Han has gone there

12:11.430 --> 12:12.270
to meet with him.

12:12.830 --> 12:13.900
He left a few days ago.

12:13.900 --> 12:15.140
You two just missed each other.

12:17.830 --> 12:19.350
I was just wondering

12:19.350 --> 12:21.430
why you were so happy these days.

12:21.860 --> 12:23.710
So you're free from his supervision.

12:24.140 --> 12:24.980
You can slack off

12:25.110 --> 12:26.020
instead of practicing.

12:27.140 --> 12:28.620
I'm not slacking off.

12:28.620 --> 12:30.070
I've brought you something urgent.

12:30.070 --> 12:30.910
Let me handle it.

12:31.430 --> 12:32.620
What's this heavy thing?

12:34.520 --> 12:35.380
Luoxian

12:35.380 --> 12:36.860
had it delivered urgently.

12:37.020 --> 12:38.070
It's said to be a present

12:38.070 --> 12:38.950
for Xu.

12:46.980 --> 12:47.860
Xu,

12:47.860 --> 12:49.500
she said the remaining 13 prefectures

12:49.500 --> 12:50.430
were all on this map.

12:52.070 --> 12:53.190
With Luozhou as a foothold,

12:53.740 --> 12:54.710
spy centers were set up

12:54.990 --> 12:55.830
and named Ziwei.

12:56.430 --> 12:57.380
This map is created

12:57.380 --> 12:58.380
based on the intelligence

12:58.380 --> 12:59.230
from all the centers

12:59.500 --> 13:00.340
in 17 Prefectures.

13:01.350 --> 13:02.780
- Great.
- Nice.

13:03.900 --> 13:04.740
It's...

13:06.590 --> 13:07.430
Impressive.

13:07.430 --> 13:12.860
(Enjoy the Beauty)

13:28.540 --> 13:29.710
General Duan,

13:29.710 --> 13:30.900
you're a hero to Shuozhou.

13:31.380 --> 13:32.900
Mr. Lin is away on business,

13:33.190 --> 13:34.110
but he ordered us

13:34.470 --> 13:35.860
to clean out his residence

13:36.140 --> 13:37.430
where you can live.

13:38.070 --> 13:40.070
To welcome you, our prefect

13:40.430 --> 13:41.990
prepared some excellent wine

13:42.190 --> 13:44.500
and had it delivered to your troops.

13:45.020 --> 13:46.710
Please accept it.

13:47.260 --> 13:48.230
According to our prefect,

13:48.660 --> 13:49.990
if you aren't satisfied

13:49.990 --> 13:50.900
with today's wine,

13:51.230 --> 13:53.430
he'll have new wine delivered tomorrow.

13:53.860 --> 13:54.860
He'll continue

13:55.070 --> 13:56.020
until you're satisfied.

14:17.310 --> 14:18.310
Bring my thanks to him.

14:19.140 --> 14:20.500
I'll have a good taste

14:20.500 --> 14:21.430
of the wine he's sent.

14:23.070 --> 14:24.140
I'll take my leave.

14:43.780 --> 14:46.470
I was ordered to serve you, General.

14:54.020 --> 14:55.470
Then why are you lowering your head?

14:56.900 --> 14:57.750
I can't even see

14:57.750 --> 14:58.670
what you look like.

15:00.110 --> 15:00.950
I...

15:04.430 --> 15:05.900
Let me serve you, General.

15:08.470 --> 15:09.540
Do you know who I am?

15:12.380 --> 15:13.230
General Duan.

15:13.900 --> 15:15.260
My name, I mean.

15:17.660 --> 15:18.540
My name is Duan Xu.

15:20.470 --> 15:21.500
Duan Shunxi.

15:33.740 --> 15:34.580
Stop it.

15:37.830 --> 15:38.670
Simu.

15:41.860 --> 15:43.740
How come you can always recognize me?

15:44.470 --> 15:45.500
I see that look

15:45.500 --> 15:46.950
when you wish to be recognized.

15:51.830 --> 15:52.900
I was passing by,

15:53.110 --> 15:53.950
so I came to see you.

15:57.140 --> 15:58.380
I made you an amulet.

15:58.590 --> 15:59.430
Take it with you.

16:01.710 --> 16:02.620
All right.

16:02.620 --> 16:03.460
Let me put it on you.

16:07.470 --> 16:08.590
The war may be dangerous,

16:09.070 --> 16:10.470
but you needn't have come

16:11.110 --> 16:12.110
in person.

16:12.950 --> 16:14.020
General Duan,

16:14.500 --> 16:16.260
hidden dangers are harder to avoid.

16:16.350 --> 16:17.190
There are problems

16:17.190 --> 16:18.260
you mortals can't solve.

16:19.710 --> 16:21.230
If you're in serious trouble,

16:21.620 --> 16:22.710
remember to summon me.

16:42.260 --> 16:43.110
Guards!

16:43.110 --> 16:43.950
No need.

16:44.110 --> 16:45.020
They can no longer

16:45.020 --> 16:45.900
hear you.

16:53.070 --> 16:54.070
Mu'ertu,

16:55.140 --> 16:56.950
do you hate to see me this much?

16:58.740 --> 17:01.070
You're merely an ousted Young Priest.

17:02.380 --> 17:03.620
What do you want?

17:04.910 --> 17:05.820
I came here

17:05.820 --> 17:07.260
to tell you one thing.

17:09.100 --> 17:11.060
Seventeen, you've been yearning for...

17:11.540 --> 17:12.470
He's back.

17:13.340 --> 17:15.060
Now he's the general of the Liang Army,

17:15.580 --> 17:16.430
Duan Xu.

17:16.430 --> 17:17.990
He's from Great Liang?

17:18.260 --> 17:19.990
Duan Xu ruined my father and me.

17:21.020 --> 17:21.870
Just like you,

17:22.390 --> 17:23.300
I want him dead.

17:25.710 --> 17:26.580
Let's work together.

17:54.630 --> 17:55.470
The All-Knowing...

17:57.100 --> 17:57.940
They were here.

18:00.020 --> 18:00.860
Who was here?

18:02.630 --> 18:04.260
Any word of Han Lingqiu?

18:05.100 --> 18:06.190
A message came yesterday.

18:06.500 --> 18:07.910
He joined General Tang in Jingzhou.

18:13.430 --> 18:15.740
What a wonderful trap to catch him!

18:17.020 --> 18:17.950
I think General Tang

18:19.780 --> 18:21.300
has been corrupted by the Chong Army.

18:22.540 --> 18:23.870
He pretended to need backup.

18:24.500 --> 18:25.580
When we reached Jingzhou,

18:26.340 --> 18:27.300
he'd work with our enemy

18:27.300 --> 18:28.140
to annihilate us.

18:29.150 --> 18:30.670
But Captain Han is in Jingzhou.

18:31.020 --> 18:32.060
With only a few soldiers.

18:32.870 --> 18:34.390
Han Lingqiu may have been detained.

18:36.340 --> 18:37.180
Meng Wan,

18:37.500 --> 18:38.580
ride to the Tabai Army

18:38.780 --> 18:39.670
and tell them

18:39.670 --> 18:40.990
not to trust Han Lingqiu's orders.

18:41.260 --> 18:42.100
Without my command,

18:42.540 --> 18:43.990
no troops can enter Jingzhou.

18:44.230 --> 18:45.070
Yes.

18:46.100 --> 18:46.940
Commandant Wu.

18:47.190 --> 18:48.100
Lead 50,000 soldiers.

18:48.260 --> 18:49.100
You leave right now.

18:49.470 --> 18:50.310
Within three days,

18:50.580 --> 18:52.060
take four cities southwest of Jingzhou.

18:52.500 --> 18:53.430
Don't worry, General.

18:53.430 --> 18:54.430
Count on me.

18:54.430 --> 18:55.430
Nothing will go wrong.

18:55.910 --> 18:57.500
I'll teach them a good lesson.

18:57.950 --> 18:58.870
Qingsheng,

18:58.870 --> 19:00.060
lead 10,000 elite soldiers.

19:00.300 --> 19:01.190
Within three days,

19:01.190 --> 19:02.150
take two eastern cities.

19:02.780 --> 19:04.020
These cities are all occupied

19:04.430 --> 19:05.630
by the Chong Army.

19:05.990 --> 19:06.830
Once you take them,

19:07.300 --> 19:08.340
you'll cut the connection

19:08.340 --> 19:09.430
between Jingzhou and Chong.

19:10.540 --> 19:11.670
I won't let you down.

19:14.910 --> 19:16.100
What about Han?

19:16.430 --> 19:17.540
Trapped in the enemy camp,

19:17.710 --> 19:18.870
he will definitely be used

19:18.870 --> 19:19.820
as a hostage.

19:19.820 --> 19:20.710
We'll save him, right?

19:21.950 --> 19:23.190
Of course we will.

19:24.540 --> 19:26.060
But we won't use our troops.

19:27.990 --> 19:28.910
You focus on the war.

19:30.300 --> 19:31.140
I'll rescue him.

19:31.670 --> 19:32.510
But...

19:37.020 --> 19:37.860
- Yes.
- Yes.

20:18.780 --> 20:19.620
Han Lingqiu.

20:20.910 --> 20:21.820
Wake up.

20:21.820 --> 20:22.660
Leave with me.

20:27.100 --> 20:28.150
It's you.

20:28.740 --> 20:30.100
Why didn't you kill me back then?

20:30.500 --> 20:31.710
Why did you save me instead?

20:32.470 --> 20:34.300
Why did you erase my memories?

20:34.870 --> 20:35.710
Why?

20:36.020 --> 20:37.190
And why did I

20:37.190 --> 20:38.150
get back my memories?

20:42.430 --> 20:43.630
Your memories are back?

20:48.260 --> 20:49.100
Han Lingqiu,

20:49.740 --> 20:50.740
think clearly.

20:52.470 --> 20:53.630
Open your eyes and look at me.

20:54.630 --> 20:55.580
I'm Duan Xu.

20:56.430 --> 20:57.390
You're Han Lingqiu.

20:57.780 --> 20:59.580
We're comrades who fight together

21:00.150 --> 21:01.670
instead of the All-Knowing assassins.

21:04.430 --> 21:05.630
I have no time to argue now.

21:06.540 --> 21:07.380
Just go with me.

21:11.950 --> 21:12.870
Duan Xu.

21:15.670 --> 21:16.540
Han Lingqiu.

21:43.060 --> 21:43.900
Mentor,

21:45.060 --> 21:45.990
how have you been?

21:47.950 --> 21:48.790
Congratulations.

21:50.630 --> 21:51.740
You've finally caught me.

21:52.910 --> 21:54.150
You saved him once.

21:55.190 --> 21:57.100
Why did you come to save him again?

21:58.710 --> 21:59.580
Why?

22:00.910 --> 22:02.100
Maybe for the same reason

22:02.100 --> 22:03.990
that I didn't kill you back then.

22:06.780 --> 22:08.230
That's the compassion

22:08.230 --> 22:09.260
you've always despised.

22:11.060 --> 22:12.020
I taught you everything,

22:12.710 --> 22:14.020
the martial arts,

22:14.020 --> 22:15.300
and the techniques.

22:15.300 --> 22:16.630
And I killed all the people

22:17.630 --> 22:18.870
you asked me to kill!

22:19.230 --> 22:20.740
Some are noble while some are humble.

22:21.580 --> 22:23.990
How could you betray me

22:23.990 --> 22:24.830
for humble ones?

22:26.060 --> 22:26.900
Mentor,

22:27.300 --> 22:28.630
there isn't an answer

22:28.630 --> 22:29.710
to everything in this world.

22:30.500 --> 22:31.950
But I can tell you this.

22:33.950 --> 22:35.740
Seventeen, your once favorite disciple...

22:36.430 --> 22:37.820
His obedience,

22:38.710 --> 22:39.550
attachment,

22:39.990 --> 22:41.950
fervor, and devotion were all fake!

22:44.190 --> 22:45.470
Always fake.

22:47.710 --> 22:49.260
I hate everything about the All-Knowing.

22:50.260 --> 22:51.870
And I never think it's an honor

22:51.870 --> 22:52.710
to be Seventeen.

22:55.540 --> 22:56.380
The truth is,

22:57.150 --> 22:58.020
I've never believed

22:58.020 --> 22:59.020
in a single god.

23:02.230 --> 23:03.780
I was the one

23:05.150 --> 23:06.060
who pulled myself

23:06.060 --> 23:07.260
out of all that misery.

23:08.780 --> 23:11.190
The god's power only exists
when I believe in him.

23:15.100 --> 23:16.230
So the god's power...

23:20.390 --> 23:21.630
Is actually my power.

23:23.300 --> 23:24.950
Cangshen won't forgive

23:25.990 --> 23:27.670
such sacrilegious words!

23:31.060 --> 23:31.900
Didn't you hear?

23:32.820 --> 23:33.780
Leave with me now.

23:34.190 --> 23:35.710
Or will you stay and be a slave?

23:37.060 --> 23:38.540
You should have been Seventeen!

23:39.060 --> 23:39.900
He's a traitor

23:39.910 --> 23:41.230
with sinister motives.

23:41.710 --> 23:43.390
He wasn't even qualified for the Trial.

23:43.740 --> 23:45.230
He ruined your life,

23:45.390 --> 23:46.500
led you down the wrong path,

23:46.500 --> 23:47.870
and made you serve your enemy!

23:48.150 --> 23:49.670
You should

23:50.020 --> 23:51.060
hate him most!

23:53.340 --> 23:54.820
Then why didn't you kill me back then?

23:55.230 --> 23:56.300
Why did you save me?

23:56.500 --> 23:57.430
Why?

23:58.990 --> 23:59.990
Catch him!

24:00.230 --> 24:01.300
Kill!

24:19.630 --> 24:20.470
(Oh no.)

25:49.150 --> 25:50.260
Kill him.

26:24.430 --> 26:25.270
Simu.

27:24.190 --> 27:25.150
Simu.

27:53.470 --> 27:54.340
Simu.

27:56.950 --> 27:57.820
Simu.

28:04.630 --> 28:05.500
I'm taking you away.

28:08.300 --> 28:09.300
Simu.

28:11.060 --> 28:12.060
Han Lingqiu.

28:13.060 --> 28:14.100
Take him away.

28:39.580 --> 28:41.060
You were just in time, Your Grace.

28:43.990 --> 28:44.990
If I hadn't sensed

28:44.990 --> 28:46.020
the amulet's abnormality,

28:46.580 --> 28:47.430
you would

28:47.430 --> 28:48.390
have been killed.

28:55.260 --> 28:56.630
Are you so worried about me?

29:00.950 --> 29:02.190
Don't act pitiful to fool me.

29:04.910 --> 29:05.870
Let me ask you.

29:08.340 --> 29:09.500
What's wrong with your body?

29:14.670 --> 29:15.510
What does that mean?

29:20.740 --> 29:21.580
Your senses

29:23.340 --> 29:24.180
have been fading.

29:30.020 --> 29:31.340
Don't overthink it, Simu.

29:32.780 --> 29:33.910
Mortals grow old.

29:34.910 --> 29:35.950
All the senses

29:36.470 --> 29:37.500
fade as well.

29:38.390 --> 29:39.260
That's normal.

29:45.740 --> 29:47.190
If you're tired of me now,

29:48.740 --> 29:49.820
what happens when I'm old?

30:15.430 --> 30:17.470
Will you really argue with a sick man?

30:20.500 --> 30:21.390
Your health...

30:23.580 --> 30:24.780
Is it really all right?

30:36.190 --> 30:37.390
Don't worry.

30:39.820 --> 30:40.780
By the way...

30:42.260 --> 30:43.100
Simu,

30:45.190 --> 30:46.670
did you kill some mortals?

30:48.870 --> 30:50.540
I kind of saw you do it.

31:10.910 --> 31:11.750
Foxy,

31:14.540 --> 31:15.380
you saw it wrong.

31:43.950 --> 31:44.790
Sleep now.

31:45.390 --> 31:47.910
When you wake up, see a doctor.

31:48.910 --> 31:49.750
Take your medicine.

31:53.580 --> 31:54.420
Promise me.

31:55.190 --> 31:56.580
Even when you're on the battlefield,

31:58.340 --> 31:59.430
you can't charge forward,

31:59.430 --> 32:00.300
regardless of safety.

32:02.340 --> 32:03.820
You must treasure your life.

32:05.580 --> 32:06.420
Understand?

32:16.230 --> 32:17.070
Simu.

32:19.740 --> 32:20.580
What's wrong?

32:36.300 --> 32:37.140
I should go.

32:44.820 --> 32:45.780
Foxy,

32:48.390 --> 32:49.230
wait until I return.

33:12.670 --> 33:13.510
Jiang Ai.

33:15.300 --> 33:16.470
Simu, what happened?

33:30.260 --> 33:31.100
It has

33:31.470 --> 33:32.710
Bai Sanxing's aura.

33:34.300 --> 33:35.140
Yes.

33:35.630 --> 33:36.870
I refined his soul candle

33:36.870 --> 33:37.820
into this.

33:38.630 --> 33:39.990
When you hold it,

33:40.710 --> 33:42.100
he'll take your orders.

33:45.190 --> 33:46.030
Simu,

33:46.780 --> 33:47.820
what do you want me to do

33:48.820 --> 33:49.820
with this thing?

33:54.190 --> 33:55.740
It's not what I want you to do,

33:57.260 --> 33:58.820
but what you truly want to do.

34:07.100 --> 34:07.940
Lady Jiang Ai,

34:10.750 --> 34:12.580
you must be cautious from now on.

34:19.700 --> 34:21.430
Greetings, Your Grace.

34:25.660 --> 34:27.310
For what reason have you summoned us

34:27.540 --> 34:28.430
so urgently?

34:29.020 --> 34:30.220
According to our decrees,

34:30.700 --> 34:32.350
how should a spirit be punished

34:32.660 --> 34:33.750
for interfering with mortals

34:34.390 --> 34:35.350
and killing mortals?

34:38.540 --> 34:39.950
According to Article 1, Section 1

34:40.220 --> 34:41.350
of 32 Golden-wall Decrees,

34:41.700 --> 34:43.310
he deserves the harshest punishment,

34:43.660 --> 34:46.060
regardless of the extent of his power.

34:57.100 --> 34:58.870
I killed mortals in the Mortal World.

35:00.140 --> 35:01.420
- What...
- By law...

35:03.910 --> 35:05.390
Punish me according to our decrees.

35:09.540 --> 35:11.060
Don't do that, Your Grace.

35:11.060 --> 35:12.350
If you're punished for violation,

35:12.500 --> 35:13.830
our world will fall into chaos!

35:14.790 --> 35:16.350
I uphold the decrees for my father.

35:16.580 --> 35:17.580
If I weren't punished,

35:17.830 --> 35:18.910
our world would be in chaos.

35:20.060 --> 35:20.990
But...

35:34.470 --> 35:35.580
Yan Ke, what do you think

35:36.990 --> 35:38.220
I should do?

35:41.910 --> 35:42.990
Considering your power,

35:43.540 --> 35:45.060
it's easy for you to kill spirits.

35:45.660 --> 35:47.020
But it's hard to make them

35:47.390 --> 35:48.230
obey you.

35:48.990 --> 35:50.430
If you defend the Golden-wall Decrees

35:50.660 --> 35:52.060
and uphold your father's justice,

35:54.060 --> 35:56.140
I beg you to set an example

35:56.430 --> 35:58.020
and take your punishment

35:58.750 --> 35:59.590
by our decrees.

36:01.220 --> 36:02.350
His Lordship...

36:09.620 --> 36:10.620
Didn't he...?

36:11.140 --> 36:12.390
Why did he say that?

37:06.950 --> 37:08.620
I interfered with mortal affairs

37:09.060 --> 37:10.020
and killed mortals.

37:11.180 --> 37:12.310
By the Golden-wall Decrees,

37:12.870 --> 37:13.830
I shall relinquish the Book of Spirits,

37:13.830 --> 37:14.870
stop using the Lantern,

37:15.660 --> 37:17.020
and take the harshest punishment.

37:19.390 --> 37:20.350
Unexpectedly, Her Grace

37:20.500 --> 37:21.340
was harsh on others,

37:22.270 --> 37:23.220
and harsher on herself.

37:23.990 --> 37:25.020
Spirits are born free.

37:26.060 --> 37:27.540
Her Grace is the Sovereign.

37:27.870 --> 37:28.750
She sacrifices herself

37:28.750 --> 37:29.700
just for these decrees.

37:30.390 --> 37:31.230
Is it worth it?

39:05.670 --> 39:09.380
♪Falling down like snow♪

39:09.850 --> 39:13.330
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

39:13.330 --> 39:17.210
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

39:17.620 --> 39:21.420
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

39:21.690 --> 39:24.360
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

39:24.520 --> 39:28.840
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

39:29.320 --> 39:32.230
♪If I could live a simple life♪

39:32.230 --> 39:33.070
♪For once♪

39:33.070 --> 39:38.150
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

39:40.240 --> 39:43.740
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

39:43.920 --> 39:47.540
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

39:48.050 --> 39:51.660
♪Let me wander through♪

39:51.660 --> 39:55.300
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

39:55.710 --> 39:59.110
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

39:59.240 --> 40:03.240
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

40:03.450 --> 40:06.140
♪As all things turn and flow♪

40:06.260 --> 40:12.170
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

40:26.260 --> 40:29.810
♪As stars shift and change places♪

40:30.060 --> 40:33.750
♪A century is like a dream♪

40:33.940 --> 40:37.520
♪Let me journey across them all♪

40:37.720 --> 40:41.210
♪Without reincarnations♪

40:41.750 --> 40:45.090
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

40:45.320 --> 40:49.140
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

40:49.320 --> 40:52.400
♪Moments may last♪

40:52.400 --> 41:00.460
♪Love and hate will fade away♪

41:57.270 --> 41:58.700
During your recuperation,

41:59.620 --> 42:00.620
I am willing

42:00.990 --> 42:01.910
to help you manage

42:03.430 --> 42:05.270
all the affairs of the Void.

42:18.060 --> 42:19.580
Don't bother.

42:21.180 --> 42:22.540
During my recuperation,

42:25.580 --> 42:26.870
all the affairs here

42:28.910 --> 42:30.270
will be handled by Jiang Ai.

42:41.270 --> 42:43.470
We shall obey, Your Grace.

43:40.281 --> 43:45.611
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:45.941 --> 43:50.191
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:51.551 --> 43:56.921
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:57.221 --> 44:01.821
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:02.911 --> 44:04.751
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:16.961 --> 44:22.401
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

44:22.581 --> 44:26.911
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:28.281 --> 44:33.671
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:33.901 --> 44:37.841
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:39.611 --> 44:41.501
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:44.161 --> 44:47.321
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:47.321 --> 44:49.851
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:49.851 --> 44:55.371
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:55.371 --> 44:58.611
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:58.611 --> 45:03.471
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

45:03.811 --> 45:06.831
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

45:06.831 --> 45:09.651
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

45:09.911 --> 45:12.441
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

45:12.441 --> 45:17.861
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

45:18.031 --> 45:21.101
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

45:21.261 --> 45:26.161
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

45:26.371 --> 45:29.841
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
